Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A new era begins,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,our High Collar Lady is determined to fight for freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and while she was on a mission to destroy that old mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the enemy line's defence was firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the commander didn't withdraw
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and training after training,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio naturally got fed up of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,While Shinobu's kindness made her heart race,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,after her bitter enemy insulted her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,she lost control once and far all, and now she's about to fight him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and show him her tomboyish combat style!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:03.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE7EB&\pos(467.027,80)\bord0\blur0.667\fs60\b1}Episode 10\NGulp down the medicine of love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't look in a good spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this little girl do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She eluded my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my spear is way better than her bamboo sword, I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go all in,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and not treat her as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If he strikes a blow... I might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 10 more centimeters \Nand my life would have been no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you be a little gentler, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you move too much, I can't apply the patches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay still for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to take care of you once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for God's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting defeated by that young girl like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It kind of reminds me of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,goes back a long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu's father, Soichirou, was still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well done! You're strong, Soichirou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And thirty years after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he abandoned Shinobu and went abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Only to never come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That Benio's look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the same as Soichirou's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, shut up! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be left alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you got shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way, go-go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's really a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? He always goes crazy if the neighbouring girl is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Nanny, big news, big news, big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you look enthusiastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,did you find a 200 yen coin?{二銭銅貨でも拾ったのか - this should be the sentence - must be because there are no 200 yen coins anymore / otherwise, just put something such as "Did something good happen?" if you want to remove specific references}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even better! I'd be richer than the God of commerce!{if I didn't mishear, he's saying 恵比寿, the God of fishing and commerce - alternatively, just remove the specific references}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anything happen to Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ranmaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny, you need to prepare a grand meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushi, tell me the good news!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After many things happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss will soon come back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!? I didn't expect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She hit that stubborn geezer with her sword
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and he floored him! You should've seen that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Lady Benio will be surely expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, to cap it all!{あたりきしゃりきかっぱのへ - if you have better ideas put them, I wanted to keep the kappa joke}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to give her a warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy, aren't you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too! Nanny, we need to have a grand dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish of her to break such a great engagement,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so frustrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, I need to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So... How is Count doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, so it was about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am really sorry for acting recklessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always been in good health,{not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so please, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than that, Benio, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I did such a thing to Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My, Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, he was pleasantly surprised by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He was surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He likes strong-arm tactics,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to him, that's way better than a simple medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, because of his stubbornness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll never openly admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you're part of our family,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go back to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with my heartbeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's something about my health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you again, hoyden.\NWhat an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My heartbeat is completely different now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:34.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,Boss Benio Greeting Party{/going to greet ...}{...お出迎えへ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the hinderance, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I have to fight her too?{not sure, but I hear 戦闘開始}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for the next schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that, there's a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that guest could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, it's me!\NHumph, you two will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to worry anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't return to this house ever again, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so it was you, Ushigorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't just stand there, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,These two damn dogs won't let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I understood, I talked too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, this is my dear henchman,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, how did you learn to do it, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything, they just grew fond of me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's hurry home before all the family members
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,can grow fond of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here just to take you home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know that Nanny made grilled chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and even Ranmaru put his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,into making roasted potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not coming home, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it be, you hit that old man on the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like that made him like me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But they still won't kick me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, even that stubborn geezer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,got won over by Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, they'll all become her henchmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let it happen! I can't be replaced!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go home, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but my mission isn't complete yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to make a mess of this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one hell of an idea! I'll join too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,by your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, scratch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you sure won't come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Grilled chicken and many delicious things are waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am weak to food, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll definitely eat them when I'll come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that I'll have to meet these dudes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, oh you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are you satisfied with just this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Real men can pull many women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an insult!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that he came to like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, men from the Meiji era were admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Very, very admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With their strength, they could afford to have multiple lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I add some milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is outrageous! You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise on behalf of Japanese women!{not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather, times have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have I been living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd go away in a snap,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:14:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She always gets nervous when it rains for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,take care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Benio!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't get married yet! Come back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, want to come back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? It's pretty noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, sorry for the loud noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't mind me, did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this rain, his neuralgia is worsening
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't look like it's going to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you call the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I tried to call him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately, he is away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Neuralgia, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny went through it too, it's a though illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any geraniums?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chinese medicine ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,swertias, chameleon plants, 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,plantagos, aractylodes, ginseng,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{Those are the same plants she is naming}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,red spider lilies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you find them and bring them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to make my medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura's special medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell is so strong that it makes those dogs run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, it's not like I'll drink it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I told that nobody must enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a medicine for your neuralgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:36.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,Shinobu{Ninja/Shinobu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just seeing your face is painful enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But my nanny recovered thanks to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,try drinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Chinese herbal medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need such an unscientific thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife only buys reliable medicines from Germany!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This works better on Japanese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink it and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this stench?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me dizzy, I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not brave enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a real man as you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,this medicine is nothing special, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what is this lizard-like thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a charred newt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A newt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A newt!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Count, you're already asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're visiting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll look after him for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go rest, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll do it by myself, you can go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake, Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You were here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I got healed by the daughter of a vassal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Count,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that might true, but that goes way before the Meiji Restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that much myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still despise vassals as a whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Before marrying me, she was in love with a vassal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should be my grandfather, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And even after she married me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,she still won't forget him no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was aware that I wasn't as handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so I tried to keep calm,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but she never stopped thinking about her first love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and could never forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How shameful,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,did you always think I was like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And to think that I even had a son with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,how shameful, how shameful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That story is just a beautiful memory of the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not like I've been dwelling in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I married you, you've always been my priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just kept on working and treating me as a bother,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,love you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, what do you think about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He has always loved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why he hates vassals so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bad impression,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but in reality, he's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:22:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could find someone who loved me that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be lovely, lovely!{reference to the first episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What an absurd guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd even marry without loving,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as he said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So give him to me!{hooray, I finally understood that she meant okure as 贈れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya want?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A lady's heart changes like wind in a storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing wrong with a High Collar Lady desiring love in the Taishou Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But where is her bluebird?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.73,0:22:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To officialise the engagement,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:22:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,an outdoor celebration is being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold on,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,our High Collar Lady doesn't know high-class manners
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and many troubles await!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it, all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a seductive maiden appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,next time on Here Comes Smart-san:\NWelcome to the party of grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,don't miss it!
